creator: Booch Studio
descriptionHtml:
Now, you can experience the latest fingertip fishing experience in the world fishing trip. With the journey, you can travel around places of interest, sea fishing, boat fishing, and show your fishing skills! Bite hook, fish! Lifelike fish, smooth and exciting fishing feel, restore the real fishing experience of tightening fishing rod for you in your mobile phone, and can compete with global fishermen in the same time, compete for the world champion, and enjoy the fun of fishing!

[GAME FEATURES]

- Diverse fishing gear systems. Travel all over the world, visit big rivers and lakes, powerful equipment will help you better adapt to different environments. According to the fishing ground change fishing gear match, constantly upgrade your fishing gear, catch bigger fish!

- Global players, synchronized competition. Wow, a saw shark! Real time leaderboard system will show the world your great achievements. The open fishing competition will test your ability as a fisherman in many aspects. Compete with the fishermen all over the world to get the place and win rich rewards. More challenge the world boss activity, witness the style of prehistoric giant beast.

- Enhanced collection system. You have been to many places and harvested many rare fish. Are you a long-standing angler? Every step of your journey has been recorded for you, and the fish atlas will show the fruitful results in different places, including the weight record! At the same time, every fish you catch can be raised, expand your private aquarium, and enjoy the precious fish you harvest at any time.

- Rich content. There are many fishing sites, from the passionate Paradise Island, to the cherry blossom coast in spring, to the picturesque virgin land, the magnificent miracle land, the brilliant Emerald City, and so on. Each fishing ground has its own unique fish species.

- The activity is wonderful. Every day, there are fishing contests and world bosses waiting for players to participate in, full-service competition. Come to show your strength. There are also mysterious ancient monsters waiting for players to challenge. Rich daily tasks, the game process is not boring.

- Show strength. Various leaderboards, and each kind of fish has its own leaderboard, looking forward to your name on the leaderboard. Sharp snout sharks, serrated sharks, king crabs, come and take photos with these handsome bosses.

- Ultimate feel. Get rid of the monotonous process of previous fishing games. The hand feeling after repeated polishing will bring you the real feeling of tightening the fishing rod, the visual pull effect, and the unique fighting mechanism, which can make your skills more diversified. Give as much space as possible so that you can be invincible in any situation through skill.

- Rich collection methods. You will take your fishing gear to famous fishing grounds around the world. All kinds of new fish will satisfy your eyes. When a rare fish is caught, it will be recorded in your personal map, including quantity and weight records. You can also check its details here. The aquarium system provides you with the opportunity to watch the fish you harvest at any time, and more importantly, you can obtain considerable resource income through training.

- An extended fishing trip. When you start your journey, you will go to five continents and four oceans, experience the unique landscape features of each region, harvest the specialty fish of each place, and experience the feeling of fishing in the middle of the sea while driving a yacht. As the journey goes on, you will go to more places, new scenes will be added, and your fishing journey will continue to extend.

More ways to play, more functions, will continue to unlock as you explore the journey, more players can participate in the world's same stage competition fishing competition! More new functions are gradually added, increasing fun and changing challenges. The world of fishing masters is waiting for you.
descriptionShort: Travel the world with your fingertips! Pack your fishing gear.
